School Assistance Application Project Scope
1. Grading Information Database
  1.1. Add classes to hold information tracking
  1.2. Remove classes
  1.3. Create a record of current and past grades
  1.4. Upload syllabus file and potentially have grading information be autofilled, support for .pdf and .docx (optional)
  1.5. Use eLearning API calls to get assignment and grading information automatically (optional)
  1.6. Manually editing any grading information in database
2. Grade Tracking
  2.1. Calculate cumulative GPA from all given class grades
  2.2. Calculate current weighted grade in a class
  2.3. Account for attendance in current weighted grade (optional)
  2.4. Allow for use of speculative future grades to predict overall class grade/to find needed passing grades
3. Other
  3.1. Zoom in/out and scroll whenever necessary
